# Basic Molecular Structures

## Simple Molecules
Water equivalent: $smiles{O}
Methane: $smiles{C}
Ethanol: $smiles{CCO}
Methanol: $smiles{CO}

## Basic Organic Compounds
Ethylene: $smiles{C=C}
Acetylene: $smiles{C#C}
Propane: $smiles{CCC}
Butane: $smiles{CCCC}

## Simple Cyclic Structures
```smiles
C1CCCCC1
```
*Cyclohexane - a six-membered ring*

```smiles
c1ccccc1
```
*Benzene - aromatic ring*

