## Size Variations

### Small
\`\`\`smiles {"width": 250, "height": 200}
CC(=O)OC1=CC=CC=C1C(=O)O
\`\`\`

### Medium
\`\`\`smiles {"width": 400, "height": 300}
CC(=O)OC1=CC=CC=C1C(=O)O
\`\`\`

### Large
\`\`\`smiles {"width": 600, "height": 450}
CC(=O)OC1=CC=CC=C1C(=O)O
\`\`\`

## Mixed Styles in One Document
Caffeine (default): $smiles{CN1C=NC2=C1C(=O)N(C(=O)N2C)C}
Caffeine (dark): $smiles{"theme": "dark"}{CN1C=NC2=C1C(=O)N(C(=O)N2C)C}
Caffeine (bold): $smiles{"bondThickness": 1.8}{CN1C=NC2=C1C(=O)N(C(=O)N2C)C}`
